\title{MPhil Individual Project}
\meta{institution}{[University of Cambridge](ucam)}
\meta{position}{Nov 2025 - Present}

\p{Supervised by [Prof. Andreas Vlachos](https://andreasvlachos.github.io/), studying whether step-level mathematical verification is better modelled as discriminative inference than generation. The project compares encoder-based verifiers with decoder-based LLMs, analyses their verification representations, and tests intervention methods for reducing shortcut-driven failures.
}